General Education courses are recommended, but not required, to support students in this major. See Group 1: Recommended General Education Courses, A and B for the selection of courses.


Chemistry (Group 3)

For some students, CHEM 107 may be substituted for CHEM 111 and CHEM 112. Before selecting the equivalent to CHEM 107, check with a Chico State major advisor.
